name: Coming Home
content: But after all I learned to fall
To hate my fear to shed my tear
憎恨我的恐惧流下我的眼泪
For all I won have said and done
为了我赢得的一切说过的话做过的事
Didn't know the way to choose
I was sparkled with broken glass
I was moving way too fast
Like a birthday card I threw away
就像我扔掉的生日贺卡
Call me stupid after all I know
说我愚蠢吧毕竟我知道
Need my time alone time to grow
需要一点独处的时间成长
雨雪交加落荒而逃从未如此狼狈
But now I'm on my way to you
但现在我在去找你的路上
